txt.en: You should talk to Tuhâl, who can be found in Utterby.
Edible plants can be found in the scrublands near Utterby.
The food stores of Utterby are beginning to run out, so the Easterlings must find a local edible flora to get by.
You should bring the edible plants to Kúlkhur, who can be found in Utterby.

'We only have a small amount of grain left in the stores, so we must find something else to eat. There must be edible plants out there somewhere, or else there would be no animals here, either. Well? What are you waiting for? Go find me some plants!'
Bring the Edible Plants to Kúlkhur
'He is right, there must be edible plants out there. Whether or not they are palatable is another matter! Let us also keep some of these plants for ourselves, to help feed my people.'
'These foul cabbages are all you could find? Perhaps the taste can be boiled off... As for you, well, at least you can follow instructions.'
